  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Rinse the chicken and pat dry with paper towels.",
    "In a large bowl, mix together achiote paste, cumin, smoked paprika, garlic, and ginger.",
    "Add the chicken to the bowl and coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Sear the chicken until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes per side.",
    "Transfer the chicken to a terracotta dish and roast in the preheated oven for 45 minutes.",
    "While the chicken is roasting, sauté the cilantro in a small pan until fragrant.",
    "Stir the cilantro into the sour cream and set aside.",
    "Remove the chicken from the oven and let rest for 10 minutes before slicing.",
    "Slice the chicken and serve with the sour cream sauce.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste."
  ],
